dmca.title: Swiss Bank Account Company Complains of Competitors' Infringement
dmca.body:
Micheloud & Cie

www.michleloud.com

Google, Inc.
Attn: Customer Support, DMCA Complaints
[private]
Mountain View, CA 94043

Lausanne, December the 5th 2003

Sent via			: Federal Express and by fax
Concerning			: Infringement of copyright notification
Original website		: www.swiss-bank-accounts.com
Infringing website 	: www.swissgates.com


Sir, I am a certified Swiss lawyer and a partner of Micheloud et Cie, a Swiss company incorporated in Lausanne, Switzerland. Our company offers services to help international clients open Swiss bank accounts. We get some of our clients through the internet with our website www.swiss-bank-accounts.com. Our company exists since 1999. We are a family business, regularly featured in Swiss and international medias. On searching on www.google.com with the search query:

"Swiss bank accounts
